*** Special Macros:
    $@      => Name of file to be made (current target name)
    $?      => Names of dependencies newer than target
    $^      => Names of all dependencies (no duplicates)
    $+      => Names of all dependencies (with duplicates)
    $<      => Name of the first dependency
    $*      => The part matched from a '%' in the target name
    $>      => ?
